description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'QUICK 10 MINUTE SPIN CLASS: TABATA HIIT | INDOOR CYCLING WORKOUT' from the channel Kirsten Allen.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: UNLOCK THE BEST YOUTUBE SPIN CLASSES: www.youtube.com/kirstenallen/join
